But I can not find this script in master branch repo too, so weird.
I try to run build_ios.sh it seems this is right, but build_all_ios_ssd.sh always fails.

@mrry Hi, thanks for watching. I am pretty sure I can access like this:
```
➜  tensorflow git:(master) ✗ ./tensorflow/contrib/makefile/build_all_ios.sh
build_all_ios.sh*      build_all_ios_ssd.sh*
```
which the `build_all_ios_ssd.sh` lying.
But I can not find this script in master branch repo too, so weird.
I try to run build_ios.sh it seems this is right, but build_all_ios_ssd.sh always fails.
